0was%20that%20nuclear%20was%20a%20dirty%2C%20if%20not%20dangerous%2C%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20times%20have%20changed%2C%20new%20insights%20and%20new%20data%20have%20emerged%2C%20and%20what%20once%20seemed%20unethical%20has%20been%20rebranded%20as%20clean%2C%20in%20every%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nuclear%20energy%20renaissance%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-google-microsoft-openai-big-tech-investment-nuclear-ai-race-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efueled%20by%20Big%20Tech%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20more%20favorable%20legislative%20climate%2C%20and%20shifting%20public%20opinion%20%E2%80%94%20hinges%20on%20a%20change%20in%20perspective%3A%20Nuclear%20energy%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20cleanest%20and%20most%20reliable%20forms%20of%20energy%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-modular-reactor-venture-capital-ai-data-centers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstruction%20of%20nuclear%20reactors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%94%20where%20nuclear%20accounted%20for%2019%25%20of%20electricity%20generated%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Energy%20Information%20Administration%20%E2%80%94%20is%20lagging%20compared%20to%20efforts%20in%20China%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20part%20of%20why%20consulting%20firms%20are%20searching%20for%20ways%20for%20nuclear%20energy%20companies%20to%20cut%20costs%2C%20improve%20efficiencies%2C%20and%20remove%20the%20obstacles%20holding%20up%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225582fa59-c003-4d7e-8023-beae74df5e8a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20sentiment%20is%20still%20a%20headwind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2094%20nuclear%20reactors%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Nuclear%20Energy%20Institute.%20And%20tech%20giants%20are%20investing%20considerably%20to%20bring%20new%20ones%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20October%2C%20Amazon%20invested%20%24500%20million%20in%20X-Energy%2C%20a%20developer%20of%20small%20nuclear%20reactors%20and%20fuel.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Google%20said%20it%20would%20purchase%20nuclear%20energy%20from%20Kairos%20Power%2C%20a%20California-based%20company%20developing%20small%20modular%20reactors.%20The%20month%20before%2C%20Constellation%20Energy%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20Microsoft%20to%20provide%20the%20tech%20giant%20with%20nuclear%20power%20for%20the%20next%20two%20decades%20by%20resurrecting%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthree-mile-island-nuclear-plant-reopens-power-microsoft-ai-push-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThree%20Mile%20Island%20nuclear%20plant%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20also%20working%20to%20jumpstart%20nuclear%20reactor%20construction%2C%20building%20on%20Biden's%20ADVANCE%20Act%20last%20year%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20remove%20regulatory%20hurdles.%20Trump%20issued%20four%20executive%20orders%20on%20Friday%20to%20accelerate%20the%20development%20of%20the%20domestic%20nuclear%20energy%20industry%2C%20touching%20on%20areas%20from%20fuel%20cycle%20development%20to%20reactor%20construction%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20licensing%2C%20to%20workforce%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20hurdles%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrowth%20in%20nuclear%20power%20is%20projected%20to%20be%20almost%20flat%20to%202050%20due%20to%20more%20stringent%20regulatory%20requirements%20than%20for%20other%20low-carbon%20energy%20sources%2C%20negative%20public%20perception%2C%20perceived%20safety%20issues%2C%20supply%20chain%20constraints%2C%20and%20uncertainty%20around%20waste%20disposal%2C%26quot%3B%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20wrote%20in%20its%202024%20Global%20Energy%20Perspective.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20persisting%20negative%20sentiment%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20concerns%20about%20how%20the%20radioactive%20waste%20that%20nuclear%20reactors%20generate%20will%20be%20stored.%20The%20federal%20government%20once%20planned%20to%20direct%20all%20waste%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-nuclear-headache%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYucca%20Mountain%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Nevada%2C%20but%20lawmakers%20and%20the%20public%20objected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20lingering%20concerns%20about%20the%20government's%20capacity%20to%20mitigate%20nuclear%20disasters%20and%20nuclear%20power's%20association%20with%20nuclear%20weapons%20proliferation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20hope%2C%20however.%20In%202024%2C%20three-quarters%20of%20respondents%2C%20out%20of%20a%20sample%20of%203.5%20million%20people%20used%20by%20Bisconti%20Research%2C%20said%20they%20favored%20the%20use%20of%20nuclear%20energy%20for%20electricity%2C%20up%20from%20about%20half%20in%20the%201980s%20and%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e702611-9f73-4a55-a097-6e40df36cc61%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20efficiency%20of%20construction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELarge-scale%20nuclear%20reactors%20require%20a%20significant%20investment%20in%20time%20and%20money.%20They%20necessitate%20significant%20upfront%20capital%20and%20require%20long%20construction%20windows%20that%20are%20often%20beset%20by%20delays%2C%20cost%20issues%2C%20and%20regulatory%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBCG%20says%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bsimpler%20the%20design%2C%20the%20better.%26quot%3B%20The%20firm%20said%20the%20optimal%20design%20should%20follow%20%26quot%3Ba%20'design-for-manufacturing'%20approach%2C%20which%20has%20delivered%20compelling%20results%20in%20other%20industries%20such%20as%20aerospace%20and%20defense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%2C%20according%20to%20BCG%2C%20should%20be%20to%20standardize%20the%20components%20and%20material%20needed%20for%20construction%2C%20along%20with%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20construction%20steps%20to%20promote%20%26quot%3Bmodularity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said.%20That%20applies%20to%20both%20large-scale%20and%20small-scale%20reactors%2C%20Benjamin%20Vannier%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20partner%20at%20BCG%2C%20told%20BI%20by%20email.%20The%20AP1000%2C%20a%20large-scale%20pressurized%20water%20reactor%2C%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20reactor%20designed%20for%20modular%20construction%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModularity%20is%20perhaps%20the%20biggest%20trend%20in%20nuclear%20right%20now.%20There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20small%20modular%20%3Cspan%3Ereactor%20companies%2C%20like%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-profit-openai-oklo-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOklo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20was%20until%20recently%20chaired%20by%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%3B%20TerraPower%2C%20which%20is%20backed%20by%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-nuclear-power-bipartisan-support-ai-clean-energy-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBill%20Gates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-invests-in-nuclear-for-aws-following-google-and-microsoft-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EX-Energy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20Amazon%20invested%20%24500%20million%20in%20last%20year.%20These%20more%20compact%20nuclear%20reactors%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20built%20in%20factories%20and%20then%20shipped%20to%20sites%20for%20installation%20and%20are%2C%20therefore%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20easier%20to%20standardize%20for%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd68b6cb-1ac4-40ee-b7ce-2ce02a21a869%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20economics%20of%20scaling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENuclear%20fission%2C%20which%20produces%20energy%20by%20splitting%20uranium%20atoms%2C%20releases%20almost%20no%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%20Many%20AI%20executives%20consider%20nuclear%20fission%20the%20only%20reliable%20way%20to%20power%20their%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20leaders%20are%20also%20excited%20by%20recent%20advances%20in%20fusion%20technology%2C%20which%20involves%20combining%20two%20atomic%20nuclei%20to%20release%20energy%20and%20is%20considered%20safer%20than%20fission.%20Type%20One%20Energy%2C%20funded%20by%20Gates%2C%20published%20research%20in%20March%20that%20shows%20there%20are%20no%20scientific%20barriers%20left%20to%20making%20commercial%20fusion%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20nuclear%20power%20remains%20only%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedium-term%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20McKinsey%20said%20in%20a%202024%20report%20on%20data%20centers%20and%20power.%20%26quot%3BThe%20timeline%20to%20scale%20nuclear%20so%20it%20can%20achieve%20rapid%2C%20repeated%20deployment%20is%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20while%20constraints%20on%20data%20center%20power%20are%20appearing%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20early%20economics%20of%20nuclear%20are%20challenging%20compared%20with%20other%20energy%20options%2C%20and%20implementing%20various%20technologies%20to%20try%20to%20reduce%20its%20costs%20may%20or%20may%20not%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epower%20plants%20are%20relatively%20cheap%20to%20run%20in%20the%20long%20term%20and%20can%20last%20as%20long%20as%2060%20years%2C%20they%20require%20considerable%20upfront%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einvestment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20report%20published%20in%202017%2C%20the%20World%20Nuclear%20Association%20said%20that%20nuclear%20plants%20are%20strongly%20influenced%20by%20capital%20cost%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20at%20least%2060%25%20of%20their%20total%20levelized%20cost%20of%20electricity%2C%20which%20is%20essentially%20a%20measure%20of%20a%20plant's%20economic%20efficiency.%20It%20is%20calculated%20by%20dividing%20the%20total%20cost%20to%20build%20and%20operate%20a%20power%20plant%20over%20its%20lifetime%20by%20the%20total%20electricity%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emay%20help%20improve%20efficiencies%20on%20the%20operating%20side.%20Rafee%20Tarafdar%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20Infosys%2C%20a%20global%20consulting%20firm%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20helping%20companies%20integrate%20AI%20into%20their%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20proof%20of%20value%20that%20we%20built%20is%3A%20How%20do%20we%20use%20all%20the%20logs%2C%20all%20the%20sensors%20that%20come%20from%20all%20these%20machines%20in%20order%20to%20triage%2C%20predict%20failures%2C%20and%20help%20resolve%20issues%20much%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20work%20the%20firm%20did%20with%20a%20large%20US%20energy%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consensus%20among%20consulting%20firms%20is%20that%20solving%20early%20construction%20bottlenecks%20is%20key%20to%20scaling%20nuclear%20energy%20as%20a%20viable%20power%20source%20for%20AI%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnuclear-power-future-obstacles-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748338261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682b1db83fe8d3928366319d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnuclear-power-future-obstacles-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nuclear%20energy%20is%20having%20a%20resurgence.%20But%20obstacles%20remain.%20Consultants%20told%20BI%20what%20they%20think%20are%20the%20key%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnuclear-power-future-obstacles-2025-5%22%2C%22