20the%20COO%20of%20our%20house.%20I%20tend%20to%20make%20more%20big-picture%20decisions%20while%20he%20carries%20out%20a%20lot%20of%20day-to-day%20tasks%2C%20and%20I%20usually%20don't%20mind%20carrying%20the%20mental%20load%20portions%20of%20the%20work%20while%20he%20turns%20thoughts%20into%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20division%20of%20labor%20that%20has%20happened%20fairly%20naturally%20based%20on%20our%20innate%20interests.%20By%20embracing%20our%20strengths%20%E2%80%94%20and%20communicating%20when%20we're%20at%20our%20capacity%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20divide%20all%20the%20necessary%20tasks%20to%20keep%20our%20household%20running%20and%20avoid%20resentment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227131a528-2e02-48ce-bcae-b78fcbfc78a9%5C%22%3EWe%20lean%20into%20our%20strengths%20at%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20for%20a%20color-coded%20calendar%20and%20anticipate%20needs%20like%20new%20shoes%20or%20doctor's%20appointments%20well%20before%20they%20come%20up.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-meets-weekly-to-meal-plan-budget-strengthen-relationship-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20to%20meal%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20am%20always%20collecting%20phone%20numbers%20from%20other%20parents%20to%20set%20up%20play%20dates%20and%20get-togethers.%20My%20husband%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20an%20excellent%20gardener%2C%20enjoys%20doing%20the%20dishes%20(something%20I'll%20never%20understand)%2C%20and%20can%20check%20to-dos%20off%20a%20task%20list%20in%20a%20slow%20and%20steady%20way%20that%20I%20find%20seriously%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20this%2C%20we%20lean%20into%20our%20strengths%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20how%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-divides-household-labor-husband-shops-and-cooks-wife-cleans-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edivide%20up%20household%20chores%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20make%20the%20menu