ars.%20I%20implement%20new%20technologies%20and%20systems%20to%20improve%20and%20modernize%20business%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20my%20company%20called%20head%20office%20staff%20back%20to%20the%20office%20four%20days%20a%20week.%20It's%20not%20a%20huge%20shift%20for%20me.%20My%20boys%20are%20university-age%2C%20so%20being%20in%20the%20office%20doesn't%20affect%20my%20ability%20to%20parent.%20I%20prep%20meals%20on%20weekends%20and%20switched%20my%20hours%20from%209-5%20to%208-4%20to%20accommodate%20walking%20the%20dogs%20and%20going%20to%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20who%20works%20from%20home%2C%20has%20stepped%20up%20to%20help%20get%20dinner%20ready%20and%20drive%20my%20youngest%20to%20school%20as%20needed.%20The%20whole%20family%20is%20pitching%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20find%20being%20back%20in%20the%20office%20helpful.%20I'm%20more%20productive%20working%20in%20the%20office%20since%20I%20can%20connect%20with%20my%20colleagues%20casually%20and%20resolve%20issues%20faster%20face%20to%20face.%20I%20feel%20more%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20find%20coming%20into%20the%20office%20enjoyable%20%E2%80%94%20I%20live%20close%2C%20so%20it's%20an%20easy%20drive%2C%20but%20for%20my%20colleagues%20who%20have%20long%20commutes%2C%20not%20so%20much.%20I%20think%20for%20families%20with%20younger%20children%2C%20it's%20adding%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20developers%20and%20analysts%20on%20our%20team%20work%20better%20at%20home%20without%20distractions.%20When%20we%20have%20deadlines%2C%20I%20get%20them%20approval%20to%20work%20from%20home%20until%20the%20coding%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20secret%20is%20finding%20a%20job%20close%20to%20home.%20I've%20seen%20feedback%20in%20our%20employee%20survey%2C%20town%20halls%2C%20and%20team%20meetings%20where%20colleagues%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20return-to-office%20policy.%20I%20presume%20the%20employee%20satisfaction%20score%20for%20some%20teams%20