e%20hard%20to%20focus.%20The%20office%20is%20great%20for%20brainstorming%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20someone%20who%20needs%20to%20sit%20down%20alone%20and%20get%20some%20work%20done%2C%20it's%20exhausting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20going%20to%20the%20office%20and%20seeing%20my%20team%2C%20but%20managers%20still%20have%20the%20flexibility%20to%20make%20decisions.%20If%20someone%20needs%20a%20day%20to%20work%20from%20home%2C%20I%20have%20no%20problem%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20a%20great%20accommodation%20process%20and%20a%20team%20that%20looks%20at%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20someone's%20life.%20We%20really%20try%20to%20do%20the%20best%20for%20our%20employees%20when%20we%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261ce1ed3-493a-4526-b73a-38871e6409a5%5C%22%3EKirstyn%20Allen%2C%2030%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22714%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20front%20of%20a%20tree%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f89b06ffb6822ec6149b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKirstyn%20Allen.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kirstyn%20Allen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAllen%20is%20a%20former%20account%20executive%20at%20Lenovo%20Inc.%20in%20Durham%2C%20North%20Carolina.%20She%20has%20one%20child%2C%20age%204.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20working%20in%20tech%20for%20about%20four%20years%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20I%20led%20a%20team%20of%20seven%20at%20Lenovo.%20As%20an%20account%20executive%2C%20my%20role%20was%20very%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20traveled%20about%20twice%20a%20month.%20Even%20when%20we%20weren't%20traveling%2C%20we'd%20work%20from%20home%20in%20the%20evenings%20after%20a%20day%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20and%20we%20went%20completely%20remote.%20My%20son%20was%20born%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20and%20so%20I%20was%20also%20able%20to%20stay%20home%20with%20him.%20By%202021%2C%20leadership%20was%20itching%20to%20get%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20sales%20floor%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20great%20message%2C%20but%20my%20life%20and%20priorities%20had%20shifted.%20Because%20COVID-19%20was%20still%20a%20concern%2C%20I%20was%20strongly%20against%20sending%20my%20son%20to%20day%20care%2C%20so%20when%20I%20heard%20the%20rumbling%2C%20I%20began%20planning%20my%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20the%20company%20wanted%20things%20back%20to%20the%20way%20they%20were%20before%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20speak%20to%20leadership%20about%20my%20concerns.%20If%20I%20thought%20they%20would've%20been%20more%20flexible%20and%20allowed%20me%20to%20work%20from%20home%20until%20my%20son%20was%20in%20school%2C%20I%20might've%20stayed.%20There%20was%20really%20no%20making%20RTO%20manageable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20married%2C%20but%20my%20husband%20works%20outside%20the%20home%20and%20never%20worked%20from%20home.%20I%20didn't%20have%20someone%20who%20could%20keep%20my%20child%20during%20the%20workday%2C%20so%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20at%20Lenovo%20in%20May%202021%20%E2%80%94%20some%20months%20before%20the%20RTO%20policy%20was%20officially%20implemented%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20fully%20remote%20position%20as%20a%20product%20marketing%20manager%20at%20Cisco.%20I%20didn't%20tell%20my%20manager%20at%20Lenovo%20I%20was%20quitting%20because%20of%20RTO%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20said%20that%20I%20had%20a%20great%20opportunity%20that%20was%20better%20for%20me%20and%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERTO%20would've%20affected%20my%20mental%20health%2C%20my%20morale%2C%20and%20my%20satisfaction%20as%20an%20employee.%20It's%20not%20that%20people%20haven't%20done%20it%20before%2C%20but%20if%20you%20have%20a%20routine%20that%20you're%20used%20to%20and%20a%20set%20way%20of%20rearing%20your%20children%2C%20RTO%20is%20going%20to%20affect%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would've%20impaired%20my%20ability%20to%20show%20up%20to%20work%20knowing%20that%20I'd%20shifted%20something%20that%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20do.%20It%20also%20has%20financial%20effects.%20Childcare%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20good%20care%20%E2%80%94%20isn't%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20were%20shown%20that%20productivity%20and%20connectivity%20don't%20suffer%20when%20employees%20work%20from%20home.%20Personally%2C%20I%20attended%20more%20meetings%20when%20we%20went%20remote%20than%20when%20I%20worked%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20enjoy%20coming%20to%20the%20office%2C%20but%20companies%20ought%20to%20create%20a%20flexible%20work%20environment%20where%20people%20can%20choose%20how%20they%20wish%20to%20show%20up%20as%20long%20as%20the%20work%20is%20getting%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20worked%20remotely%2C%20I%20could%20set%20up%20my%20son%20and%20do%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%20I%20could%20focus%20on%20work%20or%20attend%20to%20them%20when%20I%20needed%20to%2C%20and%20make%20up%20for%20that%20by%20working%20a%20little%20later%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20I%20do%20now.%20I%20have%20the%20flexibility%20to%20be%20a%20mother%20and%20an%20employee%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20giving%20that%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoms-tech-jobs-rto-changed-lives-families-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748336702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681a9203c6ad288d1480377d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoms-tech-jobs-rto-changed-lives-families-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20mothers%20with%20tech%20jobs%20share%20how%20RTO%20policies%20are%20reshaping%20their%20lives%20and%20highlighting%20the%20need%20for%20flexible%20work%20environments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Melissa%20Petro)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A88%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmo