that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErica%20McClosky%2C%20director%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20technical%20operations%20at%20Amazon%20Robotics%2C%20said%20that%20about%20300%20people%20work%20on%20the%20more%20physical%20tasks%20involved%20in%20building%20and%20maintaining%20a%20fleet%20of%20robots%20that's%20more%20than%20750%2C000%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Erica%20McClosky%20leads%20manufacturing%20for%20Amazon%20Robotics%20and%20is%20pictured%20wearing%20a%20pink%20sweater%20in%20front%20of%20Amazon's%20blue%20and%20green%20robots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f69e6ca50259add4cd081%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EErica%20McClosky%20leads%20manufacturing%20for%20Amazon%20Robotics.%3Cp%3EMadeline%20Stone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20workers%20are%20assemblers%20who%20work%20on%20the%20line%20itself.%20Another%20team%20is%20responsible%20for%20testing%20robots%20before%20they%20go%20out%20to%20fulfillment%20centers%20and%20for%20repairing%20them%20when%20they're%20experiencing%20issues.%20There%20are%20also%20employees%20who%20receive%20and%20ship%20out%20the%20materials%20needed%20to%20assemble%20the%20robots.%20Amazon%20sources%20mechanical%20parts%20from%20local%20suppliers%20as%20well%20as%20global%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20employees%20typically%20don't%20need%20advanced%20technical%20knowledge%20to%20do%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenerally%2C%20the%20requirement%20for%20us%20is%20a%20good%20attitude%2C%20ability%20to%20problem%20solve%2C%20and%20be%20curious%2C%26quot%3B%20McClosky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20those%20employees%2C%20about%20150%20engineers%20support%20and%20assist%20them.%20That%20includes%20process%20engineers%20who%20work%20alongside%20assemblers%20as%20they%20learn%20how%20to%20build%20a%20product%2C%20as%20well%20as