rk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20partner%20really%20early%20on%20to%20get%20their%20feedback%20at%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20our%20designs%20so%20that%20we're%20always%20going%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20with%20our%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitchell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Looking%20down%20on%20a%20Sequoia%20robotic%20system%20with%20blue%20totes%20inside%20Amazon%20Robotics%20facility%20in%20Westborough%2C%20Masachusetts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f6726c6ad288d1481ae89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20robot%20named%20Sequoia%20is%20a%20sortation%20and%20storage%20system.%3Cp%3EMadeline%20Stone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20recently%20opened%20a%20next-generation%20fulfillment%20center%20in%20Shreveport%2C%20Louisiana%2C%20with%2010%20times%20the%20number%20of%20robots%20than%20older%20fulfillment%20centers.%20Brady%20said%20that%2030%25%20more%20of%20the%20jobs%20in%20the%20Shreveport%20fulfillment%20center%20are%20more%20technical%20in%20nature%20than%20in%20other%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20doubt%20that%20we're%20seeing%20jobs%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Brady%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20rather%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-warehouse-robots-flatten-hiring-curve-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20robots%20replace%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Brady%20said%20that%20Amazon%20is%20committing%20significant%20resources%20to%20upskilling%20its%20employees.%20That%20includes%20technical%20apprenticeship%20programs%20and%20paying%20for%20some%20employees'%20college%20tuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20both%20people%20and%20machines%20to%20work%20together%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20this%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20blend%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%20%E2%80