%20and%20exciting%20thrill%20coursed%20through%20me%20as%20I%20wondered%20if%20I%20would%20be%20lucky%20enough%20to%20spot%20the%20elusive%20tiger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20would%20I%20cope%20with%20the%20sweltering%20heat%20and%20the%20early%20morning%20wake-up%20calls%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20heart%20raced%2C%20and%20my%20pulse%20quickened%20with%20the%20mere%20thought%20of%20witnessing%20such%20raw%20power%20in%20the%20wild%20and%20open.%20Watching%20a%20documentary%20on%20the%20legendary%20Tigress%20Queen%20of%20Ranthambore%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EMachli%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20only%20intensified%20the%20anticipation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20over%20dinner%2C%20I%20sat%20with%20the%20resort%E2%80%99s%20naturalist%20to%20plan%20the%20next%20two%20days%20of%20safaris.%20As%20we%20swapped%20tiger%20tales%20and%20trail%20maps%2C%20he%20paused%2C%20leaned%20back%2C%20and%20asked%20casually%2C%20%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20been%20to%20the%20fort%20yet%3F%20Some%20say%20it%20watches%20over%20the%20jungle%20like%20the%20original%20guardian.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smile%20that%20followed%20hinted%20that%20my%20Ranthambore%20experience%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20complete%20without%20venturing%20beyond%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F432674%2Fwildlife-photographer-sanket-reddy-lessons-nature%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuit%20of%20wildlife%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Intrigued%2C%20I%20added%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20ancient%20citadel%20to%20my%20itinerary%2C%20little%20knowing%20the%20profound%20connection%20I%20would%20feel%20to%20this%20historical%20and%20spiritual%20heart%20of%20Ranthambore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class