%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20proposed%20collection%20centres%20where%20the%20waste%20is%20segregated%20and%20organised%2C%20dry%20waste%20is%20recycled%2C%20and%20manure%20from%20the%20wet%20waste%20is%20used%20for%20kitchen%20gardens.%20We%20also%20got%20the%20contractors%20to%20train%20and%20appoint%20several%20community%20members%20for%20the%20project.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0The%20idea%20was%20to%20create%20a%20model%20that%20would%20have%20a%20sway%20over%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20waste%20disposition%20ideals.%20The%20project%20involved%20developing%20participatory%2C%20ground-up%20processes%20and%20systems%2C%20along%20with%20the%20community%2C%20BMC%20and%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDEm4IIfNC1g%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDEm4IIfNC1g%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDEm4IIfNC1g%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20G5A%20(%40g5a.culture)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Bhendi%20Bazaar%20Gharana%20Project%20aimed%20to%20bridge%20the%20cultural%20chasm%20in%20the%20legacy%20of%20Hindustani%20classical%20music.%20Parikh%20and%20the%20team%20noticed%20that%20live%20performances%20dedicated%20to%20the%20Bhendi%20Bazaar%20Gharana%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20school%20of%20Indian%20classical%20music%20(%3Cem%3Egharana%3C%2Fem%3E)%20that%20emerged%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201890%20%E2%80%94%20are%20fewer%20compared%20to%20other%20%3Cem%3Egharanas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(lineage)%20of%20Hindustani%20Classical%20Music.%20The%20reason%20could%20be%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20sixth%20generation%20of%20disciples.%20And%20the%20gharana%20was%20gradually%20slipping%20away%20unnoticed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG5A%20cityLAB%20began%20ideating%20about%20a%20portal%20dedicated%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F211990%2Fbihar-padmashri-godawari-dutta-madhubani-painting-women-empowerment-inspiring-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultural%20heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Bhendi%20Bazaar%20Gharana%2C%20where%20music%20lovers%20could%20access%20old%20recordings%2C%20archival%20data%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Egharana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20paintings%20of%20Anjanibai%20Malpekar%20the%20well%20known%20disciple%20of%20the%20gharana%2C%20who%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20muses%20of%20Raja%20Ravi%20Varma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParikh%20elaborates%20on%20their%20mentorship%20programme%2C%20which%20enabled%20three%20children%20from%20Worli%20Koliwada%20who%20were%20already%20learning%20classical%20music%20to%20engage%20with%20some%20of%20the%20practising%20musicians%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Egharana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20then%20selected%20to%20be%20mentored%20by%20Shubha%20Joshi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20disciples%20of%20this%20%3Cem%3Egharana%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20project%20%E2%80%98Reclaiming%20Shakti%E2%80%99%20in%20partnership%20with%20Akshara%20Foundation%20focused%20on%20bolstering%20the%20safety%20measures%20in%20the%20Shakti%20Mill%20area%20following%20the%20gruesome%20gang%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20photojournalist%20here%20in%202013.%20Sadly%2C%20this%20project%20did%20not%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20G5A%20cityLAB%20worked%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20D%20Ward%20of%20the%20BMC%20to%20launch%20the%20Legacy%20plaque%20project%20(honouring%20almost%20100%20cultural%2C%20political%2C%20and%20social%20community%20members%20and%20institutions%20of%20Mumbai).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20are%20just%20a%20sliver%20of%20the%20projects%20that%20G5A%20has%20championed%2C%20there%20are%20several%20more%20in%20the%20works.%20Through%20each%20of%20its%20endeavours%20within%20the%20studio%20and%20beyond%2C%20G5A%20is%20adding%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20skyline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%2C%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Anuradha%20Parikh%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748143800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D435998%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Architect%20and%20filmmaker%20Anuradha%20Parikh%20recalls%20the%20journey%20of%20breathing%20life%20into%20a%20Mumbai%20warehouse%2C%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20space%20where%20artists%20frequent%20and%20one%20that%20has%20tremendous%20social%20impact.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F435998%2Farchitect-anuradha-parikh-revamped-and-restored-g5a-warehouse-mumbai-shakti-mills-architecture-space-for-artists-theatre-plays-events-in-mumbai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Lemonade%20St