304%2Fprotect-olive-ridley-turtles-nesting-season-citizen-steps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20deep%20reverence%20for%20sea%20turtles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20evident%20in%20the%2050%20reports%20and%20papers%20he%20authored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20Whitaker%20insisted%20in%20his%20editorial%2C%20the%20legend%E2%80%99s%20generosity%20outpaced%20his%20excellence.%20He%20was%20more%20than%20the%20sum%20of%20his%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20how%20Bhaskar%E2%80%99s%20paper%20on%20sea%20turtle%20conservation%20presented%20at%20the%20World%20Conference%20on%20the%20Biology%20and%20Conservation%20of%20Sea%20Turtles%20in%201979%20became%20a%20landmark%20document%20in%20the%20history%20of%20sea%20turtle%20biology.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20bible%20for%20many%20years%20for%20the%20community.%20Satish%E2%80%99s%20article%20in%20the%20collection%20is%20the%20first%20comprehensive%20account%20of%20sea%20turtle%20nesting%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98India%20needs%20a%20Mr%20Sea%20Turtle%E2%80%99%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20could%20deter%20Bhaskar%20from%20going%20after%20what%20he%20wanted%2C%20not%20even%20his%20trigeminal%20neuralgia%20(a%20condition%20sudden%2C%20intense%2C%20electric%20shock-like%20pain%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20face).%20In%20his%2070s%2C%20while%20heading%20to%20South%20Reef%20Island%20in%20North%20Andaman%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F63528%2Fmysterious-facts-andaman-nicobar-islands%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevastated%20in%202004%20by%20a%20tsunami%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20the%20island%20where%20Bhaskar%20had%20previously%20initiated%20a%20monitoring%20programme%20for%20hawksbill%20turtles%20%E2%80%94%20the%20boat%20journey%20was%20proving%20too%20hazardous.%20It%20did%20not%20take%20more%20than%20an%20instant%20for%2